OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FThe report said: "Key issues continue
OL,8,Fto impact quality and safety ` and
OL,9,Fdisappointingly, none of them are new."
OL,11,FNicola Wise, director of secondary and
OL,12,Fspecialist care at the CQC, added:
OL,13,F"Sadly, our latest maternity
OL,14,Finspection programme has further
OL,15,Fevidenced the need for urgent action
OL,16,Fwith continued problems indicating
OL,17,Fthat the failings uncovered in recent
OL,18,Fhigh-profile investigations are not
OL,19,Fisolated to just a handful of
OL,20,Findividual trusts.
